description:
The Goddess was hurt all last season with a shoulder injury. She finished
the season ranked 5th, and has 29 [REDACTED] submissions to her name. She is
healed, she has trained, and she is ready for the championship.
Chaos is a tough, feisty, never-give-up kind of girl, just the kind we like here
at US. She fights every second of every round. We hope she will gain
experience and someday get a shot at the title herself. Until then, there will be a
lot of getting fucked like a slut on the mat.
title: The Goddess(11-7)
